Exploratory analysis

Izolda Motiejauskyte

12/1/2019

Summary

Report is splited into three parts: 1. Stand alone data sets analysis; 2. Combined information analysis; 3. Swedbank home markets (include four countries - Sweden, Lithuania, Latvia, Estonia) analysis.

Due to consistency between different data leaks we investigate only nodes that can be found in all four possible data sets. Analysis include information about entity, officer, intermediary and address nodes.
